Column.Name: Unit Price
Column.Formula: DB_LOOKUP("Item - Unit Price", "Purchase Order", HASH("Purchase Order Number", [PO Number], "Item - Number", [Item - Line Number]))

Column.Name: Amount
Column.Formula: ROUND(IF( [Item Type] = "Amount", [Received Amount] * [Item - Tax Multiplier], ([Unit Price] * [Item - Tax Multiplier]) * [Received Qty] ),2)

Column.Name: Item - Tax Multiplier
Column.Formula: IF(ISBLANK([Item - Tax Multiplier]), DB_LOOKUP("Item - Tax Multiplier", "Purchase Order", HASH("Purchase Order Number", [PO Number], "Item - Number", [Item - Line Number])), [Item - Tax Multiplier])

Column.Name: Parent Structure

TriggerCustomEvent.Description: Trigger: Clear Receipt errors (context Purchase Order)
